{"title":"We’re Giving Away Copies of the LIVE TO RIDE Book: Comment Below to Win!","link":"https://theradavist.com/live-to-ride-book/","date":1711032538000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>We brake for great cycling books. Cycling journalist <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Pflax1?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Eserp%7Ctwgr%5Eauthor\">Peter Flax</a> pinged the <a href=\"https://www.gruberimages.pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Grubers</a>, John, and others to submit photos for his new book, <a href=\"https://www.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/peter-flax/live-to-ride/9781648293917/\" target=\"_blank\">LIVE TO RIDE</a>. We got our hands on a few extra copies of this beautifully written and laid-out book, so we’re going to give two away!<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-3.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-3.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-3.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-3.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-3.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Live to ride spans the various types of cycling, from commuting to racing and the personalities in between.</p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-4.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-4.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-4.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>There are inspirational road photos from Ashley and Jared Gruber and iconic historical portraits of great cyclists like Eddy Merckx.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-2.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/LiveToRideBook-2.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Some feel-good moments captured through John’s lens over the years are sprinkled in between.</p>\n<p>We’re giving away two copies to celebrate this wonderful piece of cycling literature and visual inspiration! One will go to a random Group Ride Subscriber, and the other to a random commenter here on The Radavist.</p>\n<p>Drop a comment below to be entered to win! We’ll pick a winner next week.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/live-to-ride-book/\">We’re Giving Away Copies of the LIVE TO RIDE Book: Comment Below to Win!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"6e9036e47b6826823b4aafa550192be7a4a964e8897d9cac449c3ba6e7aca815","category":"Cycling"}